dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Christopher Thompson. May I please have your name?
Nice to meet you, Hannah. Could you provide me with your date of birth and ZIP code for verification purposes?
Sure. My date of birth is January twenty fifth nineteen eighty nine, and my ZIP code is nine zero zero two zero.
Thank you, Hannah. One last question, could you confirm the make and model of your primary vehicle?
Of course. My car is a two zero one eight Toyota Corolla.
Thank you for the information, Hannah. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now, thank you.
You're welcome, Hannah. Thank you for contacting us. Have a great day!
